{"tid":1124501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Sana紅毯慘跌　子瑜轉身神救援","createTime":"2019-04-25T05:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T07:49:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8992aab5b8fa2a6864527a2e310f93d7de3990b4","tid":1124501,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"韓國女團TWICE日前出席音樂頒獎典禮，在走紅毯時團員Sana不慎跌倒，子瑜連忙轉身救援，隨後大家也繼續保持鎮定走完紅毯。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE日前出席「The Fact Music Awards」，當天Sana穿著一襲白色長洋裝，腳踩高跟鞋，跟大家一起走上紅毯，不過途中Sana突然腳一拐，整個人就要跌倒了，走在Sana前面的子瑜，感覺到情況不對，連忙轉身伸出援手，旁邊的工作人員也趕忙前來攙扶讓Sana重新站起來，最後一行人也繼續走紅毯上台接受訪問拍照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/25/99/6220250.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2F99%2F6220250.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=70e20033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana走紅毯時不慎跌倒。 圖／擷自推特<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/04/25/99/6220252.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2F99%2F6220252.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=0b81d98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana走紅毯時不慎跌倒，子瑜轉身伸出援手。 圖／擷自推特<br />\n<br />\n真係多花神😂😂😂😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"bcb1f873fd7d94fd27d099dba4ef556070504e4a","tid":1124501,"uid":76098,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"塞左震蛋?"},{"pid":"9cf538a2ef3c9faa30070415a05053047f1dcbca","tid":1124501,"uid":60256,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"被人插到抽搐"},{"pid":"fb1454b82b5ca4f65f0b1803783730ee441726b7","t